{"tid":46571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"臨聖誕前先鬧大交","createTime":"2016-12-19T18:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T04:07:04.000Z","uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f6bc01c98708feb428028676127636008b824d","tid":46571,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"條女本身成日覺得自己好多缺點唔值得我鐘意<br />\n佢成日諗 因為佢係我第1個 所以我先會鐘意佢<br />\n如果換轉第個 我一樣會咁對第個女仔<br />\n我成日迴避 因為我覺得諗落好煩 淨係知自己呢一刻鐘意佢就夠<br />\n平時佢諗幾諗就會打完場無咩事<br />\n今日我好死唔死屎忽痕佢想搵我傾果陣我同佢講我打緊機<br />\n跟住就出左事...<br />\n佢依家話只係想等埋26號見 見埋今次唔好見<br />\n好唔想段關係就咁完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點補救好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5117b812fe9ac8ca2e83b739d7ebd28f33a4541","tid":46571,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"去搵人啦<br />\nEx都係咁 嗰時初戀唔識安慰人<br />\n都係兜野攬落去抱緊處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">慳返好多錢</span></span>"},{"pid":"20e25708c2dbbe9328bc75c97620af57d1b396e8","tid":46571,"uid":64343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:11:17.000Z","msg":"我同你女朋友好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啱啱都同男朋友嘈咗 灰矖機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2438d617eea0c7e8edad613ba49dd99342755e59","tid":46571,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去搵人啦<br />\nEx都係咁 嗰時初戀唔識安慰人<br />\n都係兜野攬落去抱緊處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">慳返好多錢</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我諗住呢2日佢收工過去搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d729168f0dd541339792b14cfa41f15c66ce50